result.adr_address: 239 Hennessy Rd, Wan Chai, Hong Kong
result.formatted_address: 239 Hennessy Rd, Wan Chai, Hong Kong
result.name: The Optimist

reviews.text: Waiters are friendly and helpful. Good Spanish food. There is a bar at ground floor with good selection of drink and cozy environment.
Service is amazing! Everyone is super friendly. The food was nice. Atmosphere was good. Loved the background music.
Great lunch buffet. Quality Spanish cold cuts and cheeses. Good menu with quality ingredients. Friendly, efficient service. Nice ambiance and decor. Highly recommended

Great atmosphere. Went for dinner with partner. Had the lobster. Grilled just right so delicious when eaten.  The steak was a touch over cooked. Asked for medium. But still nice to taste.  Staff friendly and gave good suggestions for wine pairing with meal.     Over all a good dining experience.

This is a lovely unique place with Spanish dishes. The best thing I had here was the egg flan! The steak (rib eye) was alright (a bit tough) and the lamb shank was not bad! 
Service was quick and friendly, and loved the atmosphere for the place.
